{"tid":789846,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲聽過現代愛情故事呢首歌","createTime":"2018-08-22T13:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T06:40:47.000Z","uid":92511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2526f256f5f351a25122aae4745b6a4884f359a5","tid":789846,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:58:30.000Z","msg":"聽完發現d歌詞好中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現代愛情故事<br />\n<br />\n作詞：潘偉源<br />\n作曲：李子恆<br />\n編曲：王利名<br />\n演唱：張智霖/許秋怡<br />\n<br />\n(女)別離沒有對錯 要走也解釋不多<br />\n現代說永遠已經很傻 隨著那一宵去火花已消逝<br />\n不可能付出一生那麼多<br />\n(男)情盡時就要放過 我怎會想穿心窩<br />\n若是厭棄了再不蹉跎 如共你分開應有機會再愛一個<br />\n不可能付出一生空虛過<br />\n(合)你我情如路半經過 深知道再愛痛苦必多<br />\n願你可輕輕鬆鬆放低我 剩了些開心的追憶送走我<br />\n皆因瞭解之後認清楚<br />\n離別時笑笑明晨剩我一個 瀟灑裡也會記起當初<br />\n(女)若你的心中孤單再找我<br />\n(男)若你的心窩中空虛再找我<br />\n(合)不必痛苦當憶起我<br />\n<br />\n可能因為依家同男朋友去到一個樽頸位<br />\n唔知係咪真係有將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61248a4205af369e698f037204ad7034b8aa4213","tid":789846,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25de546170f924d56498ec07c666560d07d15d8","tid":789846,"uid":4176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"現代說永遠已經很傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d866b7533b72176faa5d05d067cf9162c64bca","tid":789846,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"作為一個90後,點可能冇聽過啊？！發現新大陸咩！"},{"pid":"01ec695073e434254ed3a81103e75299f8786156","tid":789846,"uid":176657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"好好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舊歌好正<img